ER24 spokesperson Chitra Bodasing Harduth said the man who was found slumped over in the driver s seat of the vehicle which was found in Nasrec Road sustained severe injuries to the head.He was transported to hospital but his vital signs had deteriorated. Despite all efforts to save the man he sadly died as the paramedics arrived at the hospital Bodasing Harduth said. The exact details surrounding the incident are unknown. Authorities were on scene for further investigations she added.This video was shared by CICA Crime Intelligence on YouTube: 